        <span class="badge">Solutions for Every Business</span>
        <h1>Wholesale Voice <br><span class="text-gradient">Global SIP Trunking</span></h1>
        <p class="delay-1 animate-up">Premium A-Z voice termination with direct interconnects for crystal clear quality and competitive rates.</p>
        <div class="hero-cta delay-2 animate-up">
          <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">See Pricing <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline></svg></a>
